name: High technology business investment tax credit
text:
The high technology business investment tax credit provided under section 235-110.9 shall be operative for this chapter on July 1, 1999. [L 1999, c 178, §27; am L 2009, c 178, §7; am L 2017, c 3, §3]
 
Note
 
  Effect of L 2017, c 3 on tax credits.  L 2017, c 3, §8.
